Inquisitor Agravian -

A radical inquisitor slowly walks the path of corruption and heresy, 

After almost a century of killing and exterminating tyranid genestealers he began to commit an unthinkable heresy. He started using the tyranid parts to enhance his armor and improve his lethality in combat. This practice has earned him deep distain and contempt from his peers.
